l, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016605, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, whoever prepares himself or makes himself available on this day for meeting one of Your creations with the hope of reward, grace and blessings from him, then O my Master, my departure and preparation and availability and presence towards you is with the hope of Your rewards and forgiveness.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA MAN TAHAYYA-A FEE HAAZAL YAWME, AW TA-A’BBA-A AW A-A’DDA WAS-TA-A’DDA LE WEFAA-DATIN ILAA MAKHLOO-QIN, RAJAA-A RIF-DEHI WA-JAA-E-ZATE-HI WA NAWAA-FELE-HI, FA-ILAIY-KA YAA SAIYYE-DEE KAA-NAT WEFAA-DATEE WA TAHYE-ATEE WA E’DAA-DEE WAS-TE’DAA-DEE RAJAA-A RIFDE-KA, WA JAWAA-E-ZEKA WA NAWAA-FELE-KA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ مَنْ تَهَیَّاَ فِیْ هٰذَا الْیَوْمِ، اَوْ تَعَبَّأَ اَوْ اَعَدَّ وَاسْتَعَدَّ لِوِفَادَۃٍ اِلٰی مَخْلُوْقٍ، رَجَاۗئَ رِفْدِهٖ وَجَاۗئِزَتِهٖ وَنَوَافِلِهٖ، فَاِلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدِیْ كَانَتْ وِفَادَتِیْ وَتَهْیِئَتِیْ وَاِعْدَادِیْ وَاسْتِعْدَادِیْ رَجَاۗئَ رِفْدِكَ، وَجَوَاۗئِزِكَ وَنَوَافِلِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": n